rComments: Professor Rothberg is easily the best professor I've had in 4 years at this school.  He encourages new ideas and loves class discussion.  He gives you background info, then lets you take it away and ask any questions.  Anyone is foolish not to take his class.  This dude is a trauma literature GOD.

Dr. Rothberg is so _NOT_ pretensious, and he really encouraged my fellow students not to be either.  Theory was hard and he knew that, so he made sure we felt like we could ask questions, and he tried his best to answer them.  He does kind of look like Guy Smiley, but I don't think that's a bad thing.
Dr. Rothberg is fantastic!  Take him if you can.
